			<br/>
			<p>Warcraft III Reign of Chaos Installer Download: <a href="https://www.battle.net/download/getLegacy?product=WAR3&locale=en-US&os=WIN" class="noExpand"><img src="/Content/icons/Download.png" width=32 height=32></a></p>
			<p>Warcraft III The Frozen Throne Installer Download: <a href="https://www.battle.net/download/getLegacy?product=W3XP&locale=en-US&os=WIN" class="noExpand"><img src="/Content/icons/Download.png" width=32 height=32></a></p>
			<br/>
			<h3>Step 2 (Optional): Install Eurobattle.net</h3>
