			<p>Please visit the following link to get instructions on how to install Eurobattle.net</p>
			<p><a href="http://eurobattle.net/">http://eurobattle.net/</a></p>
			<br/>
			*Please do not ask us how to get a valid CDKEY for Battle.net
			<br/>
			<br/>
