        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="howtojoin">
            <h2>How to join UFW games</h2>
            <p>Click on Game List located on top of this website</p>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGameList.png" style="max-width:900px">
            <br />
            <br />
            <p>Copy the hosted game name, then join our game from custom games as shown above</p>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGameName.png">
            <br />
            <br />
            <p>Click on custom games located on top menu, type in the game name, then press enter</p>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGameLobby.png" style="max-width:900px">
            <p>And now you are ready to play!</p>
            <br />
            <br />
            <p>If you can connect to Battle.Net, come to channel Clan UFW at USEast. This is our main channel.</p>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsServer.png">
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsChannel.png">                
        </div>
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="gproxy">
            <h2>How to use GProxy</h2>
            <p>GProxy is a program that will allow you to automatically reconnect to the current game in the event of disconnections</p>
            <p>We recommend everyone to play Fate / Another III with GProxy enabled at all times</p>
            <p>Note: If you are playing from Eurobattle.net, GProxy is automatically enabled. You may skip this step.</p>
            <h3>Step 1: Download GProxy from here <a href="/download/Gproxy.zip" class="noExpand"><img class="downloadPic" src="/Content/icons/Download.png" alt="Download" width=32 height=32></a></h3>
            <h3>Step 2: Extract the zip file, open gproxy.cfg with notepad</h3>
            <h3>Step 3: Fill out the configuration file. See following image for instructions</h3>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGProxy.png" style="max-width:900px">
            <h3>Step 4: Open Warcraft 3 and go to LAN (DO NOT GO TO BATTLE.NET)</h3>
            <h3>Step 5: Launch GProxy.exe then press enter. You should see a screen similar to the following:</h3>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGProxy2.png">
            <h3>Step 6: On the GProxy console, type "/game ACTUALGAMENAME" without the quotes</h3>
            <p>ACTUALGAMENAME is where the game name goes, obtained from game list of this site</p>
            <p>Example: /game UFW Fate North America #2</p>
            <p>You should see a prompt similar to the following:</p>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGProxy3.png">
            <h3>Step 7: Join the game from LAN list in Warcraft 3. Now you are ready to play</h3>
            <img src="/Content/images/InstructionsGProxy4.png" style="max-width:900px">
        </div>
